-Uh-uh.

22:43.295 --> 22:46.198
Uh, uh... (clears throat)

22:46.232 --> 22:48.034
Um...

22:48.067 --> 22:51.538
I got you, bro.

22:51.571 --> 22:53.239
Oh.

22:53.272 --> 22:57.677
-(Becca moans)
-Oh, this is really happening.

22:57.710 --> 22:59.078
(all moaning)

23:00.647 --> 23:02.114
-Oh, yeah.
